 time in the high sucrose:low Ta treatment. We found that diet quality and Ta played an important role in the use of torpor by nectar-feeding bats.", "access_right": "restricted", "creators": [{"name": "Ayala-Berdon, Jorge", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "V\u00e1zquez-Fuerte, Rommy", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Beamonte-Barrientos, Ren\u00e9", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Schondube, Jorge E.", "affiliation": null}], "keywords": ["Biodiversity", "Mammalia", "Chiroptera", "Chordata", "Animalia", "bats", "bat"], "related_identifiers": [{"identifier": "hash://md5/075b844f21a3e1e638785a9491bb0404", "relation": "hasVersion", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "hash://sha256/2e2ecade94a01553cf28c12813523aacb4a9334638bd41173ed569bec2fc7722", "relation": "hasVersion", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "zotero://select/groups/5435545/items/2UD5JT5L", "relation": "isDerivedFrom", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "https://zotero.org/groups/5435545/items/2UD5JT5L", "relation": "isDerivedFrom", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "https://linker.bio/cut:hash://md5/9ae43a50dc151d4813d3ae81e6770bbd!/b219964-222445", "relation": "isDerivedFrom", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "hash://md5/330417efcaa2560c9b8ebcd6fae17ce0", "relation": "isPartOf", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "10.5281/zenodo.1410543", "relation": "isCompiledBy", "resource_type": "software", "scheme": "doi"}], "custom": {"dwc:class": ["Mammalia"], "dwc:kingdom": ["Animalia"], "dwc:order": ["Chiroptera"], "dwc:phylum": ["Chordata"]}, "resource_type": {"title": "Journal article", "type": "publication", "subtype": "article"}, "journal": {"issue": "5", "pages": "920-929", "title": "Journal of Experimental Biology", "volume": "220"}, "alternate_identifiers": [{"identifier": "hash://md5/075b844f21a3e1e638785a9491bb0404"}, {"identifier": "urn:lsid:zotero.org:groups:5435545:items:2UD5JT5L"}, {"identifier": "10.1242/jeb.142422"}], "communities": [{"id": "biosyslit"}, {"id": "batlit"}], "relations": {"version": [{"index"